<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<handout>
  <title>Worksheet 2.5, Matrix Factorizations</title>

  <ul marker="">

    <li workspace="1in">
      <p>(1) &#160; Compute the LU factorization for <m>A = \begin{pmatrix} -1 &amp; 5 &amp; 3 \\ 1 &amp; -10 &amp; -3 \end{pmatrix}</m>.</p>
    </li>

    <li workspace="2in">
      <p>(2) &#160; Complete the LU factorization of <m>A</m> and use it to solve <m>A\vec{x} = \vec{b}</m>.</p>

      <p>
        <me>
        A =
        \begin{pmatrix}
          2 &amp; -1 &amp; 0 \\
          -1 &amp; 2 &amp; -1 \\
          0 &amp; -1 &amp; 2
        \end{pmatrix}
        =
        \begin{pmatrix}
          1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0 \\
          -\tfrac{1}{2} &amp; 1 &amp; 0 \\
          0 &amp; -\tfrac{2}{3} &amp; 1
        \end{pmatrix}
        \begin{pmatrix}
          2 &amp; * &amp; * \\
          0 &amp; * &amp; * \\
          0 &amp; 0 &amp; *
        \end{pmatrix},
        \qquad
        \vec{b} =
        \begin{pmatrix}
          0 \\ 4 \\ -4
        \end{pmatrix}
        </me>
      </p>
    </li>

  </ul>
</handout>